  \n\n\n            Customer Question: I need assistance cancelling purchase {{Order Number}}\n            Category: ORDER\n            Intent: cancel_order\n            Support Response: I realized, you need assistance with canceling your purchase associated with the order number {{Order Number}}. I apologize for any inconvenience caused, but I assure you that I\'m here to help.\n\nTo cancel your purchase, please follow these steps:\n\n1. Log in to your account: Visit our website and log in using your credentials to access your account.\n\n2. Go to your order history: Once logged in, navigate to the "{{Online Order Interaction}}" or "{{Online Order Interaction}}" section. You will find a list of your previous purchases.\n\n3. Locate the specific purchase: Look for the purchase with the order number {{Order Number}} in your order history. Click on it to view the details.\n\n4. Initiate the cancellation: Within the purchase details, you should see an option labeled "{{Online Order Interaction}}" or something similar. Please click on that to start the cancellation process.\n\n5. Follow any additional instructions: The system may require you to provide a reason for cancellation or confirm your decision. Please provide the necessary information and follow any further instructions provided.\n\nIf you encounter any difficulties or have any questions during the cancellation process, don\'t hesitate to contact our dedicated customer support team. You can reach them during {{Customer Support Hours}} at {{Customer Support Phone Number}} or through the Live Chat feature on our website at {{Website URL}}.\n\nWe value your satisfaction and are committed to assisting you throughout the cancellation process.\n            \n\n\n            Customer Question: where do i cancel purchase {{Order Number}}\n            Category: ORDER\n            Intent: cancel_order\n            Support Response: I\'m cognizant of the fact that you\'re looking for the location where you can cancel your purchase with the purchase number {{Order Number}}. Let me guide you:\n\n1. Access the {{Online Company Portal Info}}: Begin by logging into your account on our platform.\n\n2. Locate the Order Section: Once logged in, navigate to the \'{{Online Order Interaction}}\' or \'{{Online Order Interaction}}\' tab. It should be a section where you can find all your previous purchases.\n\n3. Find the Specific Purchase: Look for the purchase with the purchase number {{Order Number}}. Select or click on it to access the purchase details.\n\n4. Initiate Cancellation: Within the purchase details page, you should see an option labeled \'{{Cancel Purchase}}\' or something similar. Please click on that to start the cancellation process.\n\n5. Confirm the Cancellation: The system may ask for confirmation or additional details to complete the cancellation. Kindly follow the instructions and provide the necessary information if prompted.\n\nIf you encounter any difficulties or have any further questions, don\'t hesitate to reach out to our dedicated customer support team. You can contact us during {{Customer Support Hours}} at {{Customer Support Phone Number}} or utilize the Live Chat feature on our {{Website URL}}. We\'re here to ensure your satisfaction every step of the way.\n            \n\n\n            Customer Question: help me to cancel my  last goddamn purchase\n            Category: ORDER\n            Intent: cancel_order\n            Support Response: I\'ve picked up that you\'re feeling frustrated and would like assistance with canceling your most recent purchase. Here\'s what you can do to cancel it:\n\n1. Sign into Your Account: Log in to your {{Online Company Portal Info}} using your credentials.\n2. Access Your Order History: Once logged in, navigate to the \'{{Online Order Interaction}}\' or \'{{Online Order Interaction}}\' section.\n3. Locate the Relevant Purchase: Look for your most recent purchase and click on it to view the details.\n4. Initiate the Cancellation Process: You should find an option labeled \'{{Online Order Interaction}}\' associated with your purchase. Click on it to start the cancellation process.\n5. Follow any Additional Steps: Depending on the platform, there may be some further instructions or questions to complete the cancellation. Follow these steps as prompted.\n\nIf you encounter any difficulties or have more questions, our dedicated support team is available during {{Customer Support Hours}}. You can reach us at {{Customer Support Phone Number}} or through the Live Chat on our website at {{Website URL}}. We value your satisfaction and will do our best to assist you."\n            \n\n\n            Customer Question: want help to cancel purchase {{Order Number}}\n            Category: ORDER\n            Intent: cancel_order\n            Support Response: I\'ve got that you\'re seeking assistance with canceling purchase {{Order Number}}, and I\'m here to guide you through the process. Rest assured, I\'ll do my best to make this experience as seamless as possible for you.\n\nTo cancel your purchase, please follow these steps:\n\n1. Sign in to your account: Visit our {{Online Company Portal Info}} and log in using your credentials.\n2. Access your order history: Once logged in, navigate to the \'{{Online Order Interaction}}\' or \'{{Online Order Interaction}}\' section.\n3. Locate the purchase: Look for the purchase associated with the order number {{Order Number}} and click on it for more details.\n4. Initiate the cancellation: You should see an option labeled \'{{Online Order Interaction}}\' or similar. Please select this option.\n5. Complete any additional steps: The system may prompt you with questions or require additional information to process the cancellation. Please provide the necessary details.\n\nIf you encounter any difficulties during the cancellation process or have any further questions, our dedicated support team is available to assist you. You can reach us during {{Customer Support Hours}} at {{Customer Support Phone Number}} or use the Live Chat feature on our website at {{Website URL}}. Your satisfaction is our priority, and we appreciate your patience and understanding throughout this process.\n            \n            \n            Provide:\n            1. Main answer\n            2. Confidence level (0-1)\n            3. Sources used\n            4. Missing information (if any)'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Intent: general_inquiry\nQuestion: I need to cancel purchase , how can i do that ?'}], 'model': 'llama-3.3-70b-versatile', 'n': 1, 'reasoning_effort': None, 'reasoning_format': None, 'service_tier': 'on_demand', 'stop': None, 'stream': False, 'temperature': 0.2}}
